      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Moonlit Espinascapade",
        "Client": "Arena Master Arlow",
        "Description": "I\u0027m back again, with another\r\ninvitation. Got an Espinas in the\r\nCitadel that needs taking care\r\nof, yeah? I\u0027m heading out tonight\r\nif you don\u0027t mind taggin\u0027 along\r\nwith an ol\u0027 geezer like me. Got\r\na little reward for you, too.",
        "Target": "Hunt an Espinas",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Espinassaut au clair de lune",
        "Client": "Ma\u00EEtre d\u0027Ar\u00E8ne Arlow",
        "Description": "H\u00E9, me revoil\u00E0 avec une autre\r\ninvitation. Un Espinas ravage\r\nla Citadelle, et je compte me\r\ncharger de lui ce soir. Il y a\r\nune belle r\u00E9compense sur lui.\r\n\u00C7a te tente d\u0027aider un vieux\r\nbriscard comme moi ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Espinas",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "L\u0027Espinas a mezzanotte",
        "Client": "Maestro Arlow",
        "Description": "Ehi, sono tornato con un altro\r\ninvito. Un Espinas sta creando\r\nscompiglio alla cittadella e ci\r\nandr\u00F2 stanotte per abbatterlo.\r\nCi sar\u00E0 una bella ricompensa.\r\nTi andrebbe di unirti a questo\r\nvecchietto?",
        "Target": "Caccia un Espinas",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Mondhelle Espinaskapaden",
        "Client": "Arenameister Arlow",
        "Description": "Hey, ich habe eine neue Einla-\r\ndung f\u00FCr dich. Ein Espinas in\r\nder Zitadelle muss in seine\r\nSchranken gewiesen werden.\r\nHast du Lust, mich alten Sack\r\nzu begleiten? Daf\u00FCr gibt es\r\nauch eine nette Belohnung. ",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Espinas.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Espinosa velada nocturna",
        "Client": "Maestro de la Arena Arlow",
        "Description": "Aqu\u00ED estoy de nuevo, con otra\r\ninvitaci\u00F3n: hay que deshacerse\r\nde un Espinas en el Basti\u00F3n.\r\nYo salgo esta noche, \u00BFte importa\r\ncazar junto a un vejete como yo?\r\n\u00A1Tengo una peque\u00F1a recompensa!",
        "Target": "Caza un Espinas",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0430 \u043F\u043E\u0434 \u043B\u0443\u043D\u043E\u0439",
        "Client": "\u041C\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0440 \u0410\u0440\u043B\u043E\u0443",
        "Description": "\u041F\u0440\u0438\u0432\u0435\u0442. \u042D\u0442\u043E \u0441\u043D\u043E\u0432\u0430 \u044F \u2014 \u0441 \u0435\u0449\u0435\r\n\u043E\u0434\u043D\u043E\u0439 \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0441\u044C\u0431\u043E\u0439. \u0412 \u0426\u0438\u0442\u0430\u0434\u0435\u043B\u0438\r\n\u0437\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0443\u0435\u0442 \u042D\u0441\u043F\u0438\u043D\u0430\u0437, \u0438 \u0432\u0435\u0447\u0435\u0440\u043E\u043C\r\n\u044F \u0438\u0434\u0443 \u043F\u043E \u0435\u0433\u043E \u0434\u0443\u0448\u0443. \u041D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u0430\r\n\u0431\u0443\u0434\u0435\u0442 \u0449\u0435\u0434\u0440\u043E\u0439. \u0415\u0441\u0442\u044C \u0436\u0435\u043B\u0430\u043D\u0438\u0435\r\n\u0440\u0430\u0437\u043C\u044F\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F \u0432\u043C\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0435 \u0441 \u0431\u044B\u0432\u0430\u043B\u044B\u043C?",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u042D\u0441\u043F\u0438\u043D\u0430\u0437\u0430",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
